Package: tAI
Type: Package
Title: The tRNA Adaptation Index
Version: 0.2.2
Date: 2025-03-19
Authors@R: person(given = c("Mario"),
                    family = "dos Reis",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "mariodosreis@gmail.com")
Description: Functions and example files to calculate the tRNA adaptation index,
  a measure of the level of co-adaptation between the set of tRNA genes and the 
  codon usage bias of protein-coding genes in a given genome. The methodology is
  described in dos Reis, Wernisch and Savva (2003) <doi:10.1093/nar/gkg897>, and 
  dos Reis, Savva and Wernisch (2004) <doi:10.1093/nar/gkh834>.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
